g":"中國轉頭俾人鏟平"},{"pid":"b001c948810e774a582543b45f46b7430a1407a4","tid":1500504,"uid":264780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:28:38.000Z","msg":"&gt; 美國又輸5G,可能輸網絡戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國華為嘅 5G 冇領先到美國，雖然華為嘅 5G 吹得好大<br />\n<br />\n總結：華為的5G宣傳水分極大，比如只說總專利數量，不談質量；華為宣稱多，實現少；號稱40多個商業合同，但只披露16個可查實的名字。根據權威分析公司的分析報告，在專利和標準、晶元、手機終端和系統設備4個領域，華為都沒有在5G技術上佔世界領先地位。今年年初任正飛才吹噓5G領先世界2-3年，毫米波（微波）技術只有華為一家在基站上做到了。很快被數據打臉：華為5G落後於世界最先水平，華為的基站出貨在毫米波是空白。 <br />\n<br />\n華為5G技術是全球領先嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/08/15/903745.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2019%2F08%2F15%2F903745.html&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=794ea48f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/08/15/903745.html</a>"},{"pid":"9e586e77ca40927cdc40a0554a300eb00a279227","tid":1500504,"uid":275648,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:29:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edd6af385632e356d42ccc875bd808fb50e478ed","tid":1500504,"uid":308201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e586e77ca40927cdc40a0554a300eb00a279227","tid":1500504,"uid":275648,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:29:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:30:33.000Z","msg":"簡體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b423f62e449347dfb78301bd193fcdc156d71fa4","tid":1500504,"uid":48531,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e2bad638a117c559f5428ada24e5eff2c9940eae","tid":1500504,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"f2140139abb967d9ba1e9d1f1dd881b0b5727257","tid":1500504,"uid":228143,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:12:28.000Z","msg":"你假膠定真心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset